    "en": {
      "title": "40,000 MT of Petrol to reach SL tonight (22)",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Ministry of Power and Energy said that a vessel carrying 40,000 MT of Petrol is scheduled to reach the country tonight (22).",
        "Also, the Ministry confirmed that a vessel carrying 40,000 MT of Diesel has reached the country last (21) night.",
        "The National Fuel Pass QR program will be implemented across the Island from Monday, the 25th of July, tweeted Minister Kanchana Wijesekera.",
        "The Minister said that the QR Code will be tested at multiple locations in Colombo from 21-24th July.",
        "Changes to the last Digit of Number Plate for Fueling \u2013 Will be effective from 21st July, Island wide.",
        "Human Rights Commission calls for probe after troops raid Sri Lanka\u2019s main protest site",
        "BASL condemns attack on protest site, calls for immediate investigation"
      ],
